#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.bitwise_or.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.bitwise\\_or"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:1 of
msgid "Compute the bit-wise OR of two tensors element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算两个张量的按位或。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:3 of
msgid ""
"Computes the bit-wise OR of the underlying binary representation of the "
"integers in the input arrays. This ufunc implements the C/Python operator"
" ``|``."
msgstr ""
"计算输入数组中整数的二进制表示的按位或。此 ufunc 实现了 C/Python 运算符 `"
"`|``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:7
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:9 of
msgid "Only integer and boolean types are handled."
msgstr "仅处理整数和布尔类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:11 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，则其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:16 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:21 of
msgid "**out** -- Result."
msgstr "**out** -- 结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`logical_or`, :py:obj:`bitwise_and`, :py:obj:`bitwise_xor`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`binary_repr`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:29 of
msgid "Return the binary representation of the input number as a string."
msgstr "以字符串形式返回输入数字的二进制表示。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:32 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitor.bitor:33 of
msgid ""
"The number 13 has the binaray representation ``00001101``. Likewise, 16 "
"is represented by ``00010000``.  The bit-wise OR of 13 and 16 is then "
"``000111011``, or 29:"
msgstr ""
"数字 13 的二进制表示为 ``00001101``。同样，16 的表示为 ``00010000``。13 "
"和 16 的按位或为 ``00011101``，即 29："

